{
  "text": "Can you tell me about what percentage is Orion influence in both the Old and the New Testaments? We prefer that this be left to the discretion of those who seek the law of one. We are not speaking in order to judge. Such statements would be construed by some of those who may read this material as judgmental. We can only suggest a careful reading and inward digestion of the contents, the understandings will become obvious.",
